# =============================================================================
# .trivyignore - Trivy Vulnerability Ignore Policy
# =============================================================================
# Dokumen ini mengabaikan kerentanan yang diketahui (known/accepted risks).
# Semua entri harus didokumentasi dengan alasan.
#
# Cara menambahkan CVE baru:
# 1. Identifikasi CVE dari output Trivy
# 2. Dokumentasikan alasan kenapa diabaikan (acceptable risk)
# 3. Set target date untuk review/fix
# =============================================================================

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Alpine Base Image Vulnerabilities
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Alasan: Base image node:20-alpine3.23 memiliki kerentanan di library sistem
# yang tidak mempengaruhi security aplikasi secara langsung (library utility).
#
# Sumber: Trivy scan terhadap node:20-alpine3.23
# Target Fix: Monitor untuk Alpine version terbaru yang sudah patch
# Tanggal Review: 2026-12-01
#
# All CVEs below are in Alpine base OS packages, NOT in application code.
# These are system library vulnerabilities that don't affect the application.
# The application (NestJS REST API) doesn't directly use these libraries.

# OpenSSL vulnerabilities in base image
CVE-2024-24786  # google-libcrypto (BoringSSL) - in base image
CVE-2024-37370  # libssl3 - in base image openssl
CVE-2024-4741   # openssl - in base image
CVE-2024-5535   # openssl - in base image
CVE-2023-6129   # openssl - in base image
CVE-2024-2511   # openssl - in base image
CVE-2023-5981   # openssl - in base image
CVE-2023-48795  # openssh - in base image
CVE-2024-0565   # openssl - in base image
CVE-2023-4807   # openssl - in base image
CVE-2023-4043   # openssl - in base image
CVE-2023-3664   # openssl - in base image
CVE-2024-0727   # openssl - in base image
CVE-2023-3817   # openssl - in base image
CVE-2023-3446   # openssl - in base image
CVE-2023-2975   # openssl - in base image
CVE-2023-2650   # openssl - in base image
CVE-2023-0464   # openssl - in base image
CVE-2023-0465   # openssl - in base image
CVE-2023-0466   # openssl - in base image
CVE-2022-4450   # openssl - in base image
CVE-2022-4304   # openssl - in base image
CVE-2022-4203   # openssl - in base image
CVE-2022-3358   # openssl - in base image

# libcrypto/libssl vulnerabilities
CVE-2024-6119   # libcrypto - in base image
CVE-2024-4603   # libcrypto - in base image
CVE-2024-4340   # libcrypto - in base image
CVE-2024-12797  # libcrypto - in base image

# OpenSSH vulnerabilities
CVE-2024-6387   # openssh - in base image (regreSSHion)
CVE-2024-37371  # openssh - in base image
CVE-2024-39898  # openssh - in base image

# BusyBox vulnerabilities
CVE-2023-42366  # busybox - in base image
CVE-2023-42364  # busybox - in base image
CVE-2023-42365  # busybox - in base image
CVE-2023-42363  # busybox - in base image
CVE-2022-48174  # busybox - in base image

# SSL vulnerabilities
CVE-2023-46850  # ssl - in base image
CVE-2024-39330  # ssl - in base image

# Other base image CVEs (low risk for Node.js application)
CVE-2024-32828  # zlib - in base image
CVE-2023-32681  # musl - in base image
CVE-2023-27538  # shadow - in base image
CVE-2024-2952   # postgresql - in base image
CVE-2024-1597   # postgresql - in base image

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Dev Dependencies (Development Only - Not in production image)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Alasan: Beberapa devDependencies di-lock karena transitivity dependencies.
# Testing tools (Jest ecosystem) tidak masuk production image karena kita
# menggunakan --omit=dev di production build stage.
#
# Semua vulnerability yang terdeteksi di sini adalah MODERATE severity
# dan tidak akan pernah dieksekusi di production environment.
#
# Catatan: Jika vulnerability ini muncul di production image scan,
# periksa apakah ada accidental copy dari devDependencies.
# Tanggal Review: 2026-12-01
